{"word":"Gibeah","slug":"gibeah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Gibeah</b> <a href=\"#/H1390\">H1390</a> <br/> 1. Of Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=57'>Jos 15:57</a><br/> 2. Of Saul, called Gibeah of Benjamin<br/> - The people's wickedness<br/> <a href='B:'></a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=9&verse=9'>Hos 9:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=28&chapter=10&verse=9'>Hos 10:9</a> <br/> - Destroyed by the Israelites<br/> <a href='B:'></a> <br/> - The city of Saul<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=10&verse=26'>1Sa 10:26</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=15&verse=34'>1Sa 15:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=6'>1Sa 22:6</a> <br/> - The ark of the covenant conveyed to, by the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=7&verse=1'>1Sa 7:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=6&verse=3'>2Sa 6:3</a> <br/> - Deserted<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=10&verse=29'>Isa 10:29</a> <br/> 3. Another town in Benjamin, called also Gibeath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=18&verse=28'>Jos 18:28</a><br/> 4. Gibeah in the field<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=20&verse=31'>Jdg 20:31</a><br/> - Probably identical with Geba<br/> <a href='S:Geba'>Geba</a> "}]}